title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Aug 23 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Aug 23 2022
description:
Investigative journalist Alex Berenson joins Clay to discuss why parents aren't getting their covid shots for their kids, the Biden Administration, Mainstream Media and Twitter conspiring to ban him from social media, and what the legacy will be of Dr. Anthony Fauci. Clay’s 5-star podcast review challenge. Callers weigh in on a variety of topics. Who should Trump pick as a vice president?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
